<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨，<delay20 />我叫<tag a="110" b="10" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是第一个来这片<colour id="1" />露营地<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />露营的人哦！</message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座岛上的居民吗？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我暂时在这儿打搅一下咯。</message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />可真不错啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先呢，就是空气很清新，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后从<tag a="110" b="32" />上观望的风景也很美<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有，居民们看起来都很幸福，太棒了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果可以住在这里，<delay20 />
感觉什么困难都能克服呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="002_01_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要试试一起住在这里吗？</message>
	<message label="002_01_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不如你也搬过来吧</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
没想到竟然存在着<delay20 />
这么令人感觉舒适的<tag a="110" b="32" />～<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到不得不离开，<delay20 />
就更流连忘返了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一起住在这里吧！</message>
	<message label="002_02_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不如你也搬过来吧</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这件事我只告诉你<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实，自从我来到这座<tag a="110" b="32" />，<delay20 />
就总感觉到强烈的视线<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家又都很热情，<delay20 />
这该不会是希望我<delay20 />
不要回去吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">来这座岛住吧</message>
	<message label="002_03_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不如你也搬过来吧</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦、可以吗？<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过随便就决定这种事，<delay20 />
真的好吗～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是这里的居民，<delay20 />
肯定认识<tag a="110" b="32" />上的管理员吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了让我能搬进这座<tag a="110" b="32" />来，<delay frames="30" />
你愿意去跟管理员商量一下吗？</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">交给我吧！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">也不是不可以</message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢！<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的命运<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就托付给你了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了让我能在这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上生活，<delay20 />
你愿意去和<tag a="110" b="32" />上的管理员<delay8 />
商量一下吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在你得到答复之前，<delay20 />
我会一直在这里等你的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，是你啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
管理员<delay20 />怎么回复你的？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等一下，<delay20 />看你的眼睛我就知道啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你真是为了我<delay20 />
付出了很多呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好吧！<delay frames="40" />
既然如此，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会相信你，<delay8 />
等着你的！！</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我能做的<delay20 />
只有默默在这里等待而已<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
但是<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你还有需要去完成的事！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你好久啦！<10_4 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
怎么样啊<tag a="110" b="0" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么？！<delay frames="40" />
你不仅和管理员商量好了，<delay20 />
还替我找到了住的地方？！<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难以置信<tag a="110" b="0" />实在是太感谢你了！<10_4 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这下子，我们就是<delay20 />
同住一座<tag a="110" b="32" />的伙伴了呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么我先回去一趟，<delay20 />
准备准备<delay20 />
开始搬家吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等好久啦！<10_4 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么<tag a="110" b="0" />
属于我的落脚处<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太棒了！<delay20 />顺利找到了呀！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样一来，我们就是生活在<delay20 />
同一座<tag a="110" b="32" />上的同伴了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么我先回一次家，<delay20 />
开始准备搬家的<delay20 />
各种事情！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨，<delay20 />你也是这座<tag a="110" b="32" />的居民？<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我此刻<delay20 />是为了搬进这座<tag a="110" b="32" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而在等待某人呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定，<delay20 />
能有机会和你做邻居呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到时候就多指教咯！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我简直迫不及待地想要<delay20 />
搬过来的那一天快些到来呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和<tag a="110" b="32" />上的大家成为好朋友之后，<delay20 />
可以一起去散步、手拉着手、<delay20 />
仰望夜空、寻找星座<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦呀，<delay20 />这简直
就是约会嘛，<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！</message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在<tag a="110" b="8" />上，<delay20 />
将会找到崭新的<tag a="110" b="10" />！<delay8 />
我有这样的预感呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然还是想要很多朋友呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被可爱的淑女们环绕<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不，<delay20 />没事。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="008_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天，我有重要的事<delay20 />
想要告诉你<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我决定搬来这座<tag a="110" b="32" />了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以后就是同一座<tag a="110" b="32" />的伙伴了，<delay20 />
请多关照呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然现在还是个露营人，<delay20 />
但我已经决定<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要搬来<tag a="110" b="9" />了。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这决定突如其来，<delay20 />
或许会让你感觉有点惊讶，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总之，请多关照啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了！<delay20 />也跟你说一声，<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我决定要搬来<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />了。<delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后就是同一座<tag a="110" b="32" />的伙伴了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请多关照呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总觉得<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay20 />
好像有点吵闹啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道说除我以外，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有其他人<delay20 />
来这座<tag a="110" b="32" />玩了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等那人回去之后<delay20 />
希望你能再来这里一趟<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想和你单独聊聊。</message>
</msbt>